12:42.717 --> 12:44.360
And Sammy of the Prophet goes, hey, good news.

12:44.400 --> 12:45.561
We're moving on from Saul.

12:45.621 --> 12:46.683
We're going to turn the page.

12:47.264 --> 12:49.667
