14:13.025 --> 14:17.511
And in verse 11, Samu says, go get him and bring him here.

14:18.432 --> 14:20.295
I will not sit down until he comes.

14:20.335 --> 14:23.379
And in this moment, David's life is going to change forever.

14:23.760 --> 14:31.911
And I wonder in this waiting time, what the conversations were like as they go get David and the brothers are all talking to each other.

14:32.772 --> 14:35.396
Was there some resentment that was creeping up in these boys?

14:36.217 --> 14:37.138
Because they know.

14:37.570 --> 14:42.297
